* Task 8b fixture: navigation/MAIN.NSP
* Demonstrates both static and dynamic FETCH navigation statements.
*
* FETCH 'TARGETPG' (static literal)
*   Expected: resolves to TARGETPG.NSP (program ObjectType)
*   EdgeKind: EdgeNavigatesTo (distinct from CALLS)
*
* FETCH #PROGVAR (dynamic variable)
*   Expected: Unresolved(ReasonDynamic), caller context preserved
*   EdgeKind: EdgeNavigatesToDynamic
*
* FR-14/FR-15: navigation edges are handled separately from module calls,
* and dynamic targets are unresolved rather than dropped.

DEFINE DATA
LOCAL
  1 PROGNAME (A20)
  1 TARGETPG (A20)
END DEFINE

* Static FETCH statement: resolves to TARGETPG.NSP.
FETCH 'TARGETPG'

* Dynamic FETCH statement: variable target, unresolvable.
FETCH #PROGVAR

END
